Package: PathSignatuR
Title: Path Signatures in R
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Simon", "Mitterhofer", , "smh@quanticfinancial.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Truncated path signatures (exact piecewise-linear) for
    multi-dimensional discrete paths. Provides an Rcpp kernel based on
    segment-wise tensor exponentials and Chen products, a pure-R
    reference for verification, time augmentation, and word enumeration
    utilities aligned with standard signature conventions.
